&lt;li&gt;&lt;a class="link" href="https://linux.die.net/man/1/socat" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
&gt;https://linux.die.net/man/1/socat&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>